title: Taking Care Of  Dirt Devil Power Duo™ Carpet and Hard Floor Cyclonic Upright
description: Sick of doing a ton of maintenance on your vacuum? The Power Duo Carpet + Hard Floor Cyclonic Vacuum (UD20125B) is as easy to clean as it is to clean with. Watch the video to see how.
